Class ContentTypesListingResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kenticocloud.delivery.ContentTypesListingResponse

  • public class ContentTypesListingResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Content types listing response

    When you retrieve a list of content items or content types from your project, the Delivery API returns a ContentTypesListingResponse

    See Also:
    DeliveryClient.getTypes(), DeliveryClient.getTypes(List)
